# Quality Standards — {{TEAM_NAME}}
_Maintained by Vigil._

## Rating Scale
- **5** — Exceptional. Ship as-is.
- **4** — Good. Minor improvements possible, ship.
- **3** — Acceptable. Meets minimum bar, ship with notes.
- **2** — Below standard. Return with specific feedback.
- **1** — Unacceptable. Full redo required.

**Rule: ≥3 delivers. <3 blocks.**

## Definition of Done by Type

### Code
- [ ] Tests pass
- [ ] Linted and formatted
- [ ] Docs/comments updated
- [ ] Error cases handled

### Architecture
- [ ] ADR written
- [ ] Pre-mortem completed
- [ ] Implementation checklist provided

### Research
- [ ] BLUF format followed
- [ ] All claims sourced
- [ ] Confidence levels stated

### Content/Documentation
- [ ] Standards compliant
- [ ] No contradictions with existing docs
- [ ] Reviewed for clarity

